{"content":"---\ntitle: \"<assemblyBinding> element for <configuration>\"\nms.date: \"03/30/2017\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"http://schemas.microsoft.com/.NetConfiguration/v2.0#configuration/assemblyBinding\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"assemblyBinding Element\"\n  - \"<assemblyBinding> Element\"\nms.assetid: 6cc55983-b894-449b-8e26-b258e53939cd\n---\n\n# \\<assemblyBinding> element for \\<configuration>\n\nSpecifies assembly binding policy at the configuration level.\n\n[**\\<configuration>**](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/configuration-element.md)   \n&nbsp;&nbsp;**\\<assemblyBinding>**\n\n## Syntax\n\n```xml\n<assemblyBinding xmlns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:asm.v1\">\n  <!-- Configuration files to include. -->\n</assemblyBinding>\n```\n\n## Attribute\n\n|           | Description |\n| --------- | ----------- |\n| **xmlns** | Required attribute.<br><br>Specifies the XML namespace required for assembly binding. Use the string \"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:asm.v1\" as the value. |\n\n## Parent element\n\n|     | Description |\n| --- | ----------- |\n| [**\\<configuration>**](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/configuration-element.md) | The root element in every configuration file used by the common language runtime and .NET Framework applications. |\n\n## Child element\n\n|     | Description |\n| --- | ----------- |\n| [**\\<linkedConfiguration>**](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/linkedconfiguration-element.md) | Specifies a configuration file to include. |\n\n## Remarks\n\nThe [**\\<linkedConfiguration>**](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/linkedconfiguration-element.md) element simplifies the management of component assemblies by allowing application configuration files to include assembly configuration files in well-known locations, rather than duplicating assembly configuration settings.\n\n> [!NOTE]\n> The **\\<linkedConfiguration>** element is not supported for applications with Windows side-by-side manifests.\n\n## Example\n\nThe following example shows how to include a configuration file on the local hard disk:\n\n```xml\n<configuration>\n  <assemblyBinding xmlns=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:asm.v1\">\n    <linkedConfiguration href=\"file://c:\\Program Files\\Contoso\\sharedConfig.xml\" />\n  </assemblyBinding>\n</configuration>\n```\n\n## See also\n\n- [Configuration file schema for the .NET Framework](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/index.md)\n","nodes":[{"pos":[4,315],"embed":true,"restype":"x-metadata","content":"title: \"<assemblyBinding> element for <configuration>\"\nms.date: \"03/30/2017\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"http://schemas.microsoft.com/.NetConfiguration/v2.0#configuration/assemblyBinding\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"assemblyBinding Element\"\n  - \"<assemblyBinding> Element\"\nms.assetid: 6cc55983-b894-449b-8e26-b258e53939cd","nodes":[{"content":"<assemblyBinding> element for <configuration>","nodes":[{"pos":[0,45],"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;assemblyBinding&gt;</ph> element for <ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;configuration&gt;</ph>","source":"<assemblyBinding> element for <configuration>"}],"path":["title"],"nosxs":false}],"yml":true},{"pos":[323,370],"content":"\\<assemblyBinding> element for \\<configuration>","linkify":"\\<assemblyBinding> element for \\<configuration>","nodes":[{"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">\\&lt;</ph>assemblyBinding&gt; element for <ph id=\"ph2\">\\&lt;</ph>configuration&gt;","pos":[0,47],"source":"\\<assemblyBinding> element for \\<configuration>"}]},{"content":"Specifies assembly binding policy at the configuration level.","pos":[372,433]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt><bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt><ph id=\"ph1\">\\&lt;</ph>configuration&gt;<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept><ept id=\"p1\">](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/configuration-element.md)</ept><ph id=\"ph2\"> </ph>","pos":[435,528],"source":"[**\\<configuration>**](~/docs/framework/configure-apps/file-schema/configuration-element.md) "},{"content":"<ph id=\"ph1\">&amp;nbsp;</ph><ph i